<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes! As a 14/15 year old girl who loved to read, I would have enjoyed this—if I were encouraged to gallop through the first few chapters to the point <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes! As a 14/15 year old girl who loved to read, I would have enjoyed this—if I were encouraged to gallop through the first few chapters to the point where Perdu and Max make a break for it. As for those who worry about sex and F-bombs, they don't know much about today's adolescents and must not remember their own adolescence.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
