              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16731747-calista?shelf=z-nina-george">z-nina-george</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1750229328" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12360113899195416720">One of my top 5 favorite books. I love it. <br/><br/>This is one of the better books I&apos;ve read this year! It is shining with delight and Nina is so good at illuminating the human condition. I hope everyone will read about the book selling apothecary Jean and his trip down the rivers of France with cats and authors and all kinds of characters.</span>
